Software Testing Business Bingo
===============================

History
-------

[kzhu91](http://twitter.com/kzhu91) and [I](http://twitter.com/jeremybmerrill) forked and editing [knorrium](http://twitter.com/knorrium)'s Business-Bingo for the Online News Association's 2011 conference in Boston.

Notes
-----

Add your words in a localization file someplace.

You will also need to add a bingoconfig.php file. Mine looks like this.

<?php

global $consumerSecret;
global $oAuthSecret;

$consumerSecret = 'Your secret here';
$oAuthSecret    = 'Your secret here';

$root_url = "http://jeremybmerrill.com/sotubingo"; #the root of the bingo directory. used for correct redirect in twittersubmit.php
?>
